data.text:
Per Florida the law, If you were born on or January 1st, 1988 and plan to drive the jet-ski or boat, your are required to have at minimum the “Florida Boating Temporary Certificate”

There is a $13.95 fee, and it is valid for 90 days

Please “CLICK” the link below to the online exam.
